Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.48,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.48,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:12.82,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:12.82,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:27.54,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:27.54,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:33.71,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:33.71,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:39.22,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:39.22,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:44.76,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:44.76,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:50.29,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:50.29,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:56.53,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:56.53,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:01:01.87,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:01:01.87,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:07.58,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:07.58,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:11.35,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:11.35,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:37.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is spacious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:40.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The area that the B Team was using opened up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:44.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a sunroom, isn't it, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:46.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:49.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad we bought this chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:54.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwako-san has transcended geezerdom and\Nis now in the realm of the old fogies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:57.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was pretty fond of Mayama, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:01.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like her child left the nest, so she suddenly aged...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:03.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll always be together, right, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:04.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe she's better like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:09.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she was like a geezer, she was the focus\Nof my admiration when I first joined...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:08.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Teshigawara Miwako of the planning department.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:15.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm really liking the way Miwako-san is right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yamazaki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The remodeling quote for the Shirakawa mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:28.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The flooring is listed as S.B. Terracotta, but\Nthat can be rather irregular in thickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You might want to switch over to ones\Nthat are 2 millimeters thinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a problem if they find out after they\Nlay it down that the door won't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:36.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand! I'll fix it right away! Yes'm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive my saying that you're better in your new form!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your geezer-ness is still in its prime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Nomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:48.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:51.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ask Yamada-san to make more bowls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:55.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's in the middle of the Hamabi Festival right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:58.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A school festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:03.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long for me I can't even remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:08.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to ask her again once the Hamabi Festival is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:10.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:15.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.64,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy115\fs31\bord0.1\shad1\be1\move(587,-111,475,140)\frz313.664\frx28\fry50\4c&H78B1C9&\3c&H8FBED2&\c&HC4ECF9&}Hamabi Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:29.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:36.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love all of you, but, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:40.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just continue to be friends, or siblings, or like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't be any more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:47.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... it's not that I think of you guys as any\Nmore or less than siblings or lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayu, I think that's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's not like that at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give them a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:57.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ippei-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's everyone doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:10.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, they were all drinking until the sun came up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for not being able to stop everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good for four guys to ask one girl all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They all knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That they'd have to give up some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're all chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:36.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They just couldn't bring themselves to ask you, and it took this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By giving this or that for excuses...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:48.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they won't want to talk to or see me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just stay the way you've been, Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure everyone's all teary-eyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a request from the chairman\Nof the Third Generation Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:03.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me out again at Christmas, Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Hagu-chan, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about Takemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:25.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:29.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was saying that he only has one interview today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So he should be back by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The closing party will be starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:37.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hungry, right, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go eat the curry that the architecture\Ndepartment is serving?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:34.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what skills I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:38.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I knew that I liked making things with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I left my house with only that interest to guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:45.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wish to accomplish by joining this company?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes! Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:53.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But four years were too short for me to get to know myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:58.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though I've already begun searching\Nfor jobs, I'm still lost and confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why I'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not because I don't have a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What I lack is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:10.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:21.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment, the 55th Hamadayama\NSchool of Art School Festival is closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:35.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto-kun! Takemoto-kun's tower is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:37.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in pieces...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:43.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, now this is rather extravagant, or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:51.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, only the person who made it could do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But this piece is going to be the foundation\Nfor the evaluation of his graduate thesis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as for that, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure done it, Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:05.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Confronting yourself and the relentless pursuit of your ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:08.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The pure soul that can never be tainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the destruction that inevitably ends it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There is not one shred of deceit in this title!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:15.56,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs20\bord0.1\b0\fscx75\fsp-1\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\frz14.827\pos(383,141)\c&H263E81&\3c&H263E81&\frx16\fry326}The Tower of\NAdolescence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray for Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:18.56,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\3c&HD5E8E7&\bord1\be1\fs56\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\shad0\pos(248,49)\frz2.45\c&H423F80&}We'll give you a 100{\fnTimes New Roman}~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:18.23,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(0,250)\3c&HD5E8E7&\bord1\be1\fs56\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\shad0\c&H423F80&\pos(401,382)\frz7.51}Keep at it,\NTakemoto-kun{\fnTimes New Roman}~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:18.23,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\3c&HD5E8E7&\bord1\be1\fs56\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\shad0\c&H423F80&\frz338.047\pos(701,334)}Ohhhh
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray for youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.69,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\shad0\bord1\be1\frx18\fry36\frz320.851\pos(462,96)\c&H5B8DB2&\3c&H94D9E9&}Hamadayama Central Avenue Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:24.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:26.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll be counting on you again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:28.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\fscx60\shad0\bord0.2\be1\fs34\c&H86B0C7&\pos(541,365)\3c&H5C6263&}bread and cake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to sell 1.2 times what we sold last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in high spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:37.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Macchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:44.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:52.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Call out to them all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:58.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a Christmas cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have tasty Christmas cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I-I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi-niichan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Use this stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichiro-oniichan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Warm up your legs with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch the flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:25.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad, Ayu? They're all so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.59,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,A plea, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:38.73,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... please... let everyone become happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Welcome! We have a white Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:45.53,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let happiness fall equally upon all of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As a special deal, all cakes are 10% off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then I'll sell for 15% off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Someone, please stop these brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:51.49,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}20% off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:54.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My store will go out of business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:59.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, why don't we start off with a toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:16.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:23.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the feeling that last year was the last time\Nwe would all gather to celebrate Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:33.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the belief that came to my mind back then was that I was\Nsupposed to be the one that would be missing this Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:38.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're thinking about right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:43.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a person like you lacks at a time\Nlike this lies in drinking and eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:44.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.84,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,250)\fs76\i1\bord2.5\be1\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\shad0\pos(428,341)\3c&HF2F5FD&\c&HB183FC&}40 minutes later
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:49.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai for Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Papayapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.80,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}nonsensical words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:51.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fubanba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, the engine's been started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan, let's play this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:56.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, the memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:10:59.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Takemoto! I challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:03.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so good, Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:06.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This game is from my generation, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Bajiter Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty, nice and smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cool, Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Gamboge Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Gamboge Nova...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:20.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little far...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\bord1.5\fs86\fscy60\fsp2\fnAlsina Ultrajada\c&H70254B&\frz38.977\pos(603,293)}Crunch{\fsp-3}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:32.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The ambulance! Call the ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:37.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:46.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have a month until our graduate thesis is due, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Morita-san is going to do about his graduate thesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:56.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all he has to do is finish up the\Nback half of that macho statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's already an eighth grader...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:02.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be expelled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:06.50,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2D1F0C&\shad0\fscy75\fs46\3c&H825A37&\pos(428,32)}expulsion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can forget about that guy, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:08.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:11.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:14.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm lost right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:22.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But, no matter how I look at it, my lost self\Nis also hopelessly an essential part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:27.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to exert everything that my current self has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:34.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's put his doubts behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:38.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's actually sort of a pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:40.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he grown up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:44.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is looking good, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:48.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best at the interviews, use that energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:49.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:57.26,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\fnArial\fscx80\shad0\be1\fsp-0.5\fs44\3c&HFFFCF1&\pos(429,362)\c&H000000&}6 hours later
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As to be expected of the super-depressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:02.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And with nothing changed, the end of the year came...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I returned home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:08.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise, to the home of my mother's new husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Happy New Year's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:16.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about a lot of things, yet acted nonchalant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In solitude, I ended up going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:25.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But my mother, betraying my predictions,\Nmelted in well with Kazu-san's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:32.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... if I can graduate and get a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:35.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ouch... what the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to work hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Work harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:44.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you so transparent, Takemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:47.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes! Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:50.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell it! The fragrant scent of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though that's all that's left to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:02.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:06.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yamada-san, Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We bought some bread for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:14.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not very...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh, a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:20.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1\fad(400,0)\shad0\bord0.8\be1\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fscy88\fs44\3c&H748B94&\c&H5F679F&\pos(159,212)}Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eh? Um, I-I'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:29.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down, Yamada-san, Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:36.69,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Hamadayama Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:37.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:38.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he has a stomach ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:42.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna be hospitalized for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:44.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We should contact his parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:45.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be here by evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:51.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan, what about Takemoto-kun's graduate\Nthesis? There aren't that many days left...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:55.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they'll wait for you in a case like\Nthis, provided you submit a form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:15:01.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But in Takemoto's case... I wonder what we should do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:07.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels heavy. My extremeties are cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this sound is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:16.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:20.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost at Mom's hospital, Yuuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:21.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:28.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... please don't rush so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll collapse first, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:34.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you just got out of the hospital last month...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:40.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad, Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They say you have the measles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You hadn't had it yet, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:54.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My father died two years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kazu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:39.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed to be having a nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:46.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find out the results of the tests tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll probably be in the hospital for about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:51.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A week?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:53.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My graduate thesis isn't done yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself so hard, Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:03.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking the entire time on my way here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:07.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think you'd be okay studying for another year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:08.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:11.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about tuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:15.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad left you plenty of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:21.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't use that money on something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:27.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it "something like this".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:39.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you two certainly are family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:42.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so overly serious and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:46.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She just won't depend on me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:49.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She says stuff like, "I can't cause you trouble."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:58.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see, every time she says that, I feel\Nlike she's saying to me, "Leave me alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:07.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you ever consider the choice of, "It'll be fine,\NKazu-san has money. Let's ask him for help?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:14.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I want you to owe me\Nsomething or push a favor onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:21.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But we came together through fate. I just want\Nyou to let me have a part in your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:27.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And a thing like that isn't called "trouble".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:37.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:38.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me study for another year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear me, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll come again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:10.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:19.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, I... I've decided to stay in\Nschool for another year and study.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:20.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:22.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll be in the same grade starting from spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to spend time together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:36.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I felt as if I talked\Nto her for the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:41.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had been that absorbed in my own issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:48.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And during that whole time, she had been worrying about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:51.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So close to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:57.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:04.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh, this is so exasperating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:12.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun! Look, a mini-TV. My gift to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:18.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The reception isn't very good... How about this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.53,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this? Or this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.62,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:21.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:24.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's the reception ceremony for the Mocademy Awards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:25.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:27.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:30.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's wearing amazing dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a festival, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:32.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is the visual effects award.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Space Titanic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about it. The CG is supposed to be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The space aliens are really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:44.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a little vicious, but that's what's cute about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:52.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they kind of look like Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-They don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:56.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the acceptance speech is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:58.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, those are fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how they're always a little strained.
